LMH YHVH Th'yMD BUrChVQ Th'yLYM L'yThVTh BTShUrH.
BG'aVTh UrSh'y YDLQ 'yNY YThPhShV BMZMVTh ZV ChShBV.
KY-HLL UrSh'y 'yL-Th'aVTh NPhShV VBTSh'y BUrK N'aTSh YHVH.
UrSh'y KGBH 'aPhV BL-YDUrSh 'aYN 'aLHYM KL-MZMVThYV.
YChYLV DUrKV BKL-'yTh MUrVM MShPhTYK MNGDV KL-TShVUrUrYV YPhYCh BHM.
'aMUr BLBV BL-'aMVT LDUr VDUr 'aShUr L'a-BUr'y.
'aLH PhYHV ML'a VMUrMVTh VThK ThChTh LShVNV 'yML V'aVN.
YShB BM'aUrB ChTShUrYM BMSThUrYM YHUrG NQY 'yYNYV LChLKH YTShPhNV.
Y'aUrB BMSThUr K'aUrYH BSKH Y'aUrB LChTVPh 'yNY YChTPh 'yNY BMShKV BUrShThV.
VDKH YShCh VNPhL B'yTShVMYV ChLK'aYM.
'aMUr BLBV ShKCh 'aL HSThYUr PhNYV BL-Ur'aH LNTShCh.
QVMH YHVH 'aL NSh'a YDK 'aL-ThShKCh 'yNYYM.
'yL-MH N'aTSh UrSh'y 'aLHYM 'aMUr BLBV L'a ThDUrSh.
Ur'aThH KY-'aThH 'yML VK'yS ThBYT LThTh BYDK 'yLYK Y'yZB ChLKH YThVM 'aThH HYYTh 'yVZUr.
ShBUr ZUrV'y UrSh'y VUr'y ThDUrVSh-UrSh'yV BL-ThMTSh'a.
